A Division II Men's Basketball Tournament|Basketball]] (1): [[2010_NCAA_Division_II_Men%27s_Basketball_Tournament|2010]]\n** [[NCAA Men's Division II Cross Country Championship|Cross country]] (1): 1983\n\n*'''Women's (7)'''\n** [[NCAA Division II Women's Basketball Tournament|Basketball]] (5): 1982, 1985, 1986, 2001, 2002\n** [[NCAA Women's Division II Tennis Championship|Tennis]] (2): 1991, 1992\n\n'''Results'''\n\n{|class=\"wikitable\" width=\"50%\"\n|- align=\"center\" \n{{CollegePrimaryHeader|team=Cal Poly Pomona Broncos|School year|Sport|Opponent|Score}} \n|- align=\"center\" bgcolor=\"\"\n| 1975\u201376 || Baseball || [[Southern Illinois University Edwardsville|SIU Edwardsville]] || 17\u20133\n|- align=\"center\" bgcolor=\"\"\n| 1979\u201380 || Baseball || [[University of New Haven|New Haven]] || 13\u20136\n|- align=\"center\" bgcolor=\"\"\n| 1981\u201382 || Women's basketball || [[Tuskegee University|Tuskegee]] || 93\u201374\n|- align=\"center\" bgcolor=\"\"\n| 1982\u201383 || Baseball || [[Jacksonville State University|Jacksonville State]] || 9\u20137\n|- align=\"center\" bgcolor=\"\"\n| 1983\u201384 || Men's cross country || [[St. Cloud State University|St. Cloud State]] || 86\u2013100\n|- align=\"center\" bgcolor=\"\"\n| 1984\u201385 || Women's basketball || [[University of Central Missouri|Central Missouri]] || 80\u201369\n|- align=\"center\" bgcolor=\"\"\n| 1985\u201386 || Women's basketball || [[North Dakota State University|North Dakota State]] || 70\u201363\n|- align=\"center\" bgcolor=\"\"\n| 1990\u201391 || Women's tennis || [[University of California, Davis|UC Davis]] || 5\u20133\n|- align=\"center\" bgcolor=\"\"\n| 1991\u201392 || Women's tennis || [[Grand Canyon University|Grand Canyon]] || 5\u20130\n|- align=\"center\" bgcolor=\"\"\n| 2000\u201301 || Women's basketball || [[University of North Dakota|North Dakota]] || 87\u201380\n|- align=\"center\" bgcolor=\"\"\n| 2001\u201302 || Women's basketball || [[Southeastern Oklahoma State University|S