st of Nominees | publisher=iHeartRadio | date=January 9, 2019 | accessdate=January 9, 2019}}</ref>\n|-\n|}\n\n== Japan Gold Disc Awards ==\nThe Japan Gold Disc Awards (\u65e5\u672c\u30b4\u30fc\u30eb\u30c9\u30c7\u30a3\u30b9\u30af\u5927\u8cde) for Music sales in the [[Recording Industry Association of Japan]], is major music awards held annually in Japan also released as a CD. Little Mix have received two awards out of two nominations.\n{{awards table}}\n!{{Abbr|Ref.|Reference}}\n|-\n| rowspan=\"2\" align=\"center\"| 2014\n| rowspan=\"2\"| Little Mix\n| Best 3 New Artists\n| {{won}}\n| rowspan=\"2\" align=\"center\"| <ref name=\"Japan Gold Disc Awards\">{{cite web|author=Japan Gold Disc Awards|title=Best New Artist International|year=2014|url=http://www.golddisc.jp/award/28/index.html}}</ref>\n|-\n| New Artist of the Year\n| {{won}}\n|}\n\n==MTV Awards==\n\n===MTV Europe Music Awards===\nThe [[MTV Europe Music Awards]] was established in 1994 by [[MTV Europe]] to award the music videos from European and international artists.<ref>{{cite web|url = http://www.capitalfm.com/events/mtv-emas/photos/best-moments/|title = Photos: MTV EMA Most Memorable Moments|publisher = [[Capital (radio network)|Capital FM]]|accessdate = 15 February 2015}}</ref> Little Mix has received 4 awards from 8 nominations.\n{{awards table}}\n!{{Abbr|Ref.|Reference}}\n|-\n| rowspan=\"1\" align=\"center\"| 2014\n| rowspan=\"8\"| Little Mix\n|rowspan=\"2\"|Best UK & Ireland Act\n| {{nominated}}\n| rowspan=\"1\" align=\"center\"| <ref name=\"c\" />\n|-\n| rowspan=\"2\" align=\"center\"| 2015\n| {{won}}\n| rowspan=\"2\" align=\"center\"| <ref name=\"c\">{{cite web|url=http://uk.mtvema.com/_/little-mix|title=MTV EMA 2015 Little Mix|}}</ref>\n|-\n| Worldwide Act: Europe\n| {{nom}}\n|-\n| rowspan=\"1\" align=\"center\"| 2016\n| rowspan=\"4\"| Best UK & Ireland Act\n| {{won}}\n| rowspan=\"1\" align=\"center\"| <ref name=\"c\" />\n|-\n| rowspan=\"1\" align=\"center\"| 2017\n| {{nom}}\n| rowspan=\"1\" align=\