tthias|title=The Mamas and The Papas: Flower-Power-Ikonen, Psychedelika und sexuelle Revolution|date=December 2014|publisher=ibidem-Verlag, ibidem Press|language=German|isbn=978-3-8382-6577-3|page=17}}</ref> \n{{awards table}}\n!{{Abbr|Ref.|Reference}}\n|-\n!scope=\"row\"|2013\n|rowspan=\"3\"|Little Mix\n|Newcomer of the Year \n|{{Won|place=Gold}}\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"|<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.bravo.de/sport/bravo-otto-wahl-part-3-waehle-die-bffs-und-das-hot-couple-262953.html|title=BRAVO Otto-Wahl&nbsp;\u2013 Part 3: W\u00e4hle die BFFs und das Hot Couple|work=Bravo|accessdate=September 18, 2018|date=January 15, 2014|language=German|url-status=live|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160920161813/http://www.bravo.de/sport/bravo-otto-wahl-part-3-waehle-die-bffs-und-das-hot-couple-262953.html|archivedate=September 20, 2016}}</ref>\n|-\n!scope=\"row\"|2018\n|rowspan=\"2\"|Best Band/Duo\n|{{Nominated}}\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"|<ref>{{cite web |title=BRAVO-Otto-Wahl 2018: Vote f\u00fcr deinen Star! |url=https://www.bravo.de/bravo-otto-wahl-2018-vote-fuer-deinen-star-379763.html |website=Bravo |accessdate=24 October 2018 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20181024213844/https://www.bravo.de/bravo-otto-wahl-2018-vote-fuer-deinen-star-379763.html |archivedate=24 October 2018 |language=German}}</ref>\n|-\n!scope=\"row\"|2019\n|{{Won|place=Gold}}\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"|<ref>{{cite web |title=BRAVO-Otto-Wahl 2019: Vote f\u00fcr deinen Star! |url=https://www.bravo.de/bravo-otto-wahl-2019-vote-fuer-deinen-star-382841.html |website=[[Bravo (magazine)|Bravo]]|accessdate=23 October 2019 |language=German}}</ref>\n|}\n\n==Brit Awards==\nFirst awarded in 1977, the [[Brit Awards]] are the highest profile music awards ceremony in the UK recognizing popular music and sponsored by [[MasterCard]].<ref>{{cite web|title=BRITs Duo On Track To Reach Dizzee-ing Heights in UK Charts, 19 February 2010|url=http://bpi.co.uk/press-area/news-amp3b-press-release/article/brits-duo-on-track-to-reach-dizzee-ing-heights-in-uk-charts.aspx|publisher=[[British Phonographic Industry]]|accessdate=16 June 2015|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20100922212152/http://bpi.co.uk/press-area/news-amp3b-press-release/article/brits-duo-on-track-to-reach-dizzee-ing-heights-in-uk-charts.aspx|archivedate=22 September 2010}}</ref> Little Mix has received two awards from nine nominations.\n{{awards table}}\n!{{Abbr|Ref.|Reference}}\n|-\n|rowspan=\"3\" align=\"center\"| 2016 \n|-\n|rowspan=\"2\"| \"[[Black Magic (Little Mix song)|Black Magic]]\"\n| British Single of the Year\n| {{nominated}}\n| rowspan=\"2\" align=\"center\"| <ref name=\"b\">{{cite web|url=http://www.capitalfm.com/brits/news/2016-nominations/#DIXpCPQSyVQizc7C.97|title=BRIT Awards 2016 Nominations|work = CapitalFM |publisher=CapitalFM|date=14 January 2016|accessdate=14 January 2016}}</ref>\n|-\n| British Video of the Year\n| {{nominated}}\n|-\n|rowspan=\"4\" align=\"center\"| 2017\n|-\n| Little Mix\n| British Group\n| {{nominated}}\n| rowspan=\"3\" align=\"center\"| <ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.billboard.com/articles/news/7697649/brit-awards-2017-winners-list|title=Brit Awards 2017: See the Full Winners List|work = Billboard|date=22 February 2017|accessdate=1 April 2017}}</ref>\n|-\n|-\n|\"[[Shout Out to My Ex]]\"\n| British Single of the Year\n| {{won}}\n|-\n|\"[[Hair (Little Mix song)|Hair]]\" <small>(featuring [[Sean Paul]])</small>\n| British Video of the Year\n| {{nominated}}\n|-\n| rowspan=\"2\" align=\"center\"| 2018\n| rowspan=\"2\" |\"[[Touch (Little Mix song)|Touch]]\"\n|British Single of the Year\n| {{nominated}}\n| <ref>{{cite web |last1=Hedges-Stocks |first1=Zach |title=The Complete Guide to the Brit Awards 2018 |url=https://www.telegraph.co.uk/music/news/complete-guide-brit-awards-2018/ |website=The Telegraph |accessdate=12 January 2019}}</ref>\n|-\n|British Video of the Year\n| {{nominated}}\n| <ref>{{cite web |last1=Hedges-Stocks |first1=Zach |title=The C